    "description": "<strong>Pedalverse：山地自行车与无人机大师的邂逅</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/f6b396586d9cd8748220103c41c81627.poster.avif?t=1736747834\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/f6b396586d9cd8748220103c41c81627.webm?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/f6b396586d9cd8748220103c41c81627.mp4?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>体验突破性的极限运动融合，让您掌控小径和天空。无论您是渴望山地自行车下坡的刺激寻求者，还是准备掌握 FPV 无人机特技艺术的科技爱好者，Pedalverse 都提供了一个广阔的开放世界，冒险无止境。<br><br>在这款游戏中，肾上腺素永远不会停止。在不同的天气条件下穿越不同的地形，从阳光明媚的山峰到雾气笼罩的山谷，或者切换齿轮飞上天空，执行不受重力影响的自由式无人机特技。在每次骑行和飞行中，Pedalverse 都会挑战您突破极限，提供与您所征服的环境一样动态且不可预测的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/a835c919641f1cfaefb98282f1583415.poster.avif?t=1736747834\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/a835c919641f1cfaefb98282f1583415.webm?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/a835c919641f1cfaefb98282f1583415.mp4?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要特点:<br><u>日夜循环</u>：在一天中的任何时间体验赛车的快感。选择一天中您最喜欢的时间或让游戏中的时钟自然循环。无论您喜欢黎明的光芒、正午的阳光还是神秘的夜晚，选择权都在您手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/d440308e1acc94eb1a6934158f00ea1e.poster.avif?t=1736747834\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/d440308e1acc94eb1a6934158f00ea1e.webm?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/d440308e1acc94eb1a6934158f00ea1e.mp4?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>动态天气</u>：实时面对动态天气条件。无论您是在雪地里驰骋、在大雨中航行，还是在享受晴朗的晴天，您都可以自定义天气或让它动态变化，以应对每次新的挑战。<br><br><u>双重游戏玩法</u>：在 MTB 速降赛车和 FPV 无人机特技之间无缝切换。穿越充满挑战的赛道或飞上天空进行惊心动魄的自由式机动——每种模式都提供独特而令人兴奋的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/8d9054dd5478ce9e8d668870ab7a0335.poster.avif?t=1736747834\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/8d9054dd5478ce9e8d668870ab7a0335.webm?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164680/extras/8d9054dd5478ce9e8d668870ab7a0335.mp4?t=1736747834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>巨大的开放世界</u>：探索充满动态轨道的广阔而多样的景观。每个区域都提供独特的挑战，从陡峭的山坡到适合无人机杂技表演的开阔场地。<br><br><u>挑战和活动</u>：通过保持动作新鲜感的挑战和活动来测试您的技能。<br><br>Pedalverse 不仅仅是一款游戏，它还是冒险家和寻求刺激者的游乐场。你会征服山路，主宰天空，还是两者兼而有之？在 Pedalverse 中，选择权在你！",
